<nav class="nav" id="nav" data-screen-label="Nav"><svg class="sunmark" viewBox="0 0 32 32" aria-hidden="true"><circle class="sun-disc" cx="16" cy="16" r="10"></circle></svg><a class="wm" href="/">AMPM <small>BUILDING SERVICES</small></a><div class="links"><a href="/services/" class="">Services</a><a href="/work/" class="">Work</a><a href="/compliance/" class="">Compliance</a><a href="/about/" class="active">About</a><a href="/contact/" class="">Contact</a></div><a class="phone" href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></nav><div class="page"><div class="shell"><section class="sec p-hero"><div class="reveal in"><div class="kicker">About</div></div><h1 class="reveal d1 in">The building-services<br>arm of AMPM Group.</h1><p class="lede reveal d2 in">AMPM Building Services holds MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks under one entity, run on the operating stack, compliance posture and audit framework of AMPM Group — <strong>the holding company built around Gemini AMPM, the life-safety flagship trading since 1997.</strong></p></section><section class="sec"><div class="intro2 reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 36px;"><div><div class="kicker">How we operate</div><h2 class="dhead">Four operating<br>principles.</h2></div><p class="body">The discipline a Tier-1 buyer or a sophisticated end-user needs to see before they trust a brand-new contractor with a package.</p></div><div class="principles reveal in"><div class="principle"><div class="n">01</div><div><h4>One contractor, four lines.</h4><p>MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks all sit under AMPM Building Services. One Form of Tender, one PM, one snag list, one team to hold to the programme. The complexity of coordinating multiple sub-contractors stops at our door, not yours.</p></div></div><div class="principle"><div class="n">02</div><div><h4>Compliance is a posture, not an afterthought.</h4><p>Golden-thread documentation, audit-ready records, RAMS and method statements on every package. The framework comes from AMPM Group — refined across nearly three decades of life-safety and fire work — not invented on the job.</p></div></div><div class="principle"><div class="n">03</div><div><h4>Tier-1 application discipline.</h4><p>We understand how Tier-1 main-contractor application cycles work and tighten our own cadence to match. No over-application drift, no late-stage commercial surprises, no awkward conversations with the QS.</p></div></div><div class="principle"><div class="n">04</div><div><h4>Operating stack of an established group.</h4><p>Procore for delivery, Uptick for asset and PPM, Microsoft 365 for golden-thread documentation, Xero for financials. Above-market for our scale — already operating across the Group, and Building Services runs on it.</p></div></div></div></section></div><section class="band ink" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="shell"><div class="intro2 reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 40px;"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Part of AMPM Group</div><h2 class="dhead sm" style="color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">One mothership.<br>Six shapes.</h2></div><p class="body" style="color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.86);">AMPM Group is a compliance-led building-services group: Gemini AMPM at the centre, and a set of subsidiaries that extend the offering. We are the in-house building-services arm.</p></div><div class="grp-grid reveal in"><div class="cell"><span class="tag">The flagship</span><h3>Gemini AMPM</h3><p>Fire, security, passive fire and life-safety since 1997. Employee-owned. NSI Gold, BAFE, FIRAS, Constructionline Gold and more.</p></div><div class="cell current"><span class="tag">This entity</span><h3>AMPM Building Services</h3><p>MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks. One accountable contractor across the building-services scope most clients procure separately.</p></div><div class="cell"><span class="tag">The wider Group</span><h3>Facilities · Live · Academy</h3><p>Aggregated FM, the AMPM Live client portal, and the Group's training and accreditation arm. Six companies, one mothership, one palette.</p></div></div><div class="grp-chips reveal in"><a class="grp-chip" href="https://geminiampm.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">Gemini AMPM</a><a class="grp-chip current" href="/">AMPM Building Services</a><a class="grp-chip" href="https://www.ampmgroup.co.uk/companies/ampm-facilities/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AMPM Facilities</a><a class="grp-chip" href="https://www.ampmgroup.co.uk/companies/ampm-live/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AMPM Live</a><a class="grp-chip" href="https://www.ampmgroup.co.uk/companies/ampm-ventures/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AMPM Ventures</a><a class="grp-chip" href="https://www.ampmgroup.co.uk/companies/ampm-academy/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">AMPM Academy</a></div></div></section><div class="shell"><section class="sec"><div class="reveal in" style="margin-bottom: 32px;"><div class="kicker">Leadership</div><h2 class="dhead sm">The hands on the tiller.</h2><p class="body" style="margin-top: 14px;">Senior leadership shared with AMPM Group. Operational delivery and site teams sit underneath — full team structure available with PQQ responses.</p></div><div class="team reveal in"><div class="person"><div class="role">Group Managing Director</div><div class="name">Dan Small</div><p class="note">Group Managing Director of AMPM Group, carrying the director role for Building Services. Operational lead across delivery, supply chain and team. Twenty-plus years in M&amp;E and building services.</p></div><div class="person"><div class="role">Group Chair</div><div class="name">Jamie Dawson</div><p class="note">Chair of AMPM Group and sponsor of Building Services. Co-founder of Gemini AMPM (1997). Holds the Group's client, investor and acquisition relationships.</p></div><div class="person"><div class="role">Group Commercial Director</div><div class="name">Luke Finney</div><p class="note">Group commercial lead. Owns the pricing, estimating and commercial discipline that runs through Building Services. Twenty-plus years on the commercial side of M&amp;E and life-safety.</p></div></div></section></div><section class="band green" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="shell"><div class="cta-split reveal in"><div><div class="kicker on-dark">Approach us</div><h2 class="dhead sm">The next step<br>is a conversation.</h2><p class="body" style="margin-top: 18px;">Tier-1 pre-qualification, direct quotation, supplier onboarding or a role on the team.</p></div><div class="cta-row2" style="flex-direction: column; align-items: flex-start;"><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">Get in touch →</a><a class="btn ghost" href="/contact/">General enquiry</a></div></div></div></section></div><footer class="foot" data-nav-dark="true"><div class="foot-inner"><div><div class="fwm">AMPM</div><span class="fmer" aria-hidden="true"><span style="background: var(--m-green);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-purple);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-orange);"></span><span style="background: var(--m-blue);"></span></span><p class="ftag">MEPH, Commercial, Fabric and Groundworks — one accountable contractor for London and the South East. The building-services arm of AMPM Group.</p></div><div><h5>Site</h5><ul><li><a href="/">Home</a></li><li><a href="/services/">Services</a></li><li><a href="/work/">Work</a></li><li><a href="/compliance/">Compliance</a></li><li><a href="/about/">About</a></li><li><a href="/contact/">Contact</a></li></ul></div><div><h5>Direct lines</h5><ul><li><a href="mailto:tenders@ampm.co.uk">tenders@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:hello@ampm.co.uk">hello@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:suppliers@ampm.co.uk">suppliers@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="mailto:careers@ampm.co.uk">careers@ampm.co.uk</a></li><li><a href="tel:03300430080">0330 043 0080</a></li></ul></div><div><h5>AMPM Group</h5><ul><li><a href="https://ampmgroup.co.uk" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">ampmgroup.co.uk ↗</a></li><li><a href="